Then, with the innovative Elumina8 technology, every detail of the new GLK becomes visible one by one, to form a unified image.
With this promotion, Mercedes is undoubtedly trying to introduce something new into the stereotypical advertising world of the automotive industry.
Can this attract the interest of prospective customers? We will see.
